OL,3,CParcel problems reach record as 15
OL,4,Cmillion people are let down on the
OL,5,Cdoorstep
OL,7,FThe most common problems people faced
OL,8,Fwith their last delivery included the
OL,9,Fdriver leaving before they had time to
OL,10,Fget to the door (29%), their parcel
OL,11,Fbeing left in an insecure location
OL,12,F(24%) and parcels arriving late (24%).
OL,14,FCitizens Advice said its findings
OL,15,Fshowed there had been "marginal"
OL,16,Fchanges in scores over the last five
OL,17,Fyears, but the overall picture was one
OL,18,Fof consumers being "persistently
OL,19,Ffailed" by parcel companies.
