OL,7,FThe charity's league table looks at
OL,8,Fthe top five delivery companies by
OL,9,Fparcel volume and measures their
OL,10,Fperformance against criteria including
OL,11,Fcustomer service, delivery problems
OL,12,Fand how well they meet accessibility
OL,13,Fneeds, such as people needing louder
OL,14,Fknocking or longer to answer the door.
OL,16,FScores achieved by firms for
OL,17,Faccessibility worsened this year,
OL,18,Fdespite a new condition by Ofcom
OL,19,Frequiring firms to give disabled
OL,20,Fconsumers the opportunity to report
OL,21,Ftheir accessibility needs.
