OL,7,FComplaints and customer service
OL,8,Frankings remained stagnant, with
OL,9,Falmost half (47%) of those who had
OL,10,Fexperienced a problem with their
OL,11,Fdelivery facing a further issue trying
OL,12,Fto resolve the problem, such as a slow
OL,13,Fresponse, issues with automated
OL,14,Fsystems such as a chat bot and having
OL,15,Fto contact a firm multiple times to
OL,16,Fget a response.
