OL,7,FOfcom introduced guidance on
OL,8,Fcomplaints and accessibility in 2023,
OL,9,Fbut Citizens Advice said its research
OL,10,Fand Ofcom's own findings showed many
OL,11,Fparcel firms were still ignoring the
OL,12,Frules.
OL,14,FCitizens Advice said it was calling on
OL,15,FOfcom to monitor performance and fine
OL,16,Fthe worst offenders.
