OL,7,F"Our league table has tracked parcel
OL,8,Fproblems from warehouse to doorstep.
OL,9,FWe continue to see millions of people
OL,10,Fchasing lost parcels, having their
OL,11,Faccessibility needs ignored and
OL,12,Fhitting a brick wall when they try to
OL,13,Fcomplain.
OL,15,F"The question now is whether the
OL,16,Fregulator will take tougher action to
OL,17,Fimprove the parcel market once and for
OL,18,Fall."
