OL,7,FAn Ofcom spokesman said: "We have a
OL,8,Fstrong track record of holding parcel
OL,9,Ffirms to account on behalf of the
OL,10,Fpublic. That has involved tracking
OL,11,Fpeople's experiences of parcel
OL,12,Fdeliveries for over a decade, and, as
OL,13,Fa result, introducing strengthened
OL,14,Fregulations on parcel firms in 2023.
OL,16,F"Under these rules, postal operators
OL,17,Fmust have a simple and transparent
OL,18,Fcomplaints process in place, and have
OL,19,Fclear and effective policies and
OL,20,Fprocedures for the fair treatment of
OL,21,Fdisabled customers.
